<section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 max-w-4xl">
        <h2
            class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-ultimate-navy text-center mb-16"
        >
            Seputar Ultimate Education
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
            <details
                class="accordion-item group border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm"
                open=""
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 list-none font-bold text-ultimate-navy dark:text-white"
                >
                    Apakah bergabung menjadi partner berbayar?
                    <span
                        class="material-symbols-outlined text-ultimate-blue transition-transform duration-300 expand-icon"
                        >expand_more</span
                    >
                </summary>
                <div
                    class="p-6 pt-0 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 leading-relaxed"
                >
                    Tidak, bergabung menjadi partner Ultimate Education adalah
                    100% gratis tanpa biaya pendaftaran apapun.
                </div>
            </details>
            <details
                class="accordion-item group border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 list-none font-bold text-ultimate-navy dark:text-white"
                >
                    Kapan komisi akan dibayarkan?
                    <span
                        class="material-symbols-outlined text-ultimate-blue transition-transform duration-300 expand-icon"
                        >expand_more</span
                    >
                </summary>
                <div
                    class="p-6 pt-0 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 leading-relaxed"
                >
                    Komisi akan dibayarkan setiap tanggal 5 di bulan berikutnya
                    setelah siswa melakukan pelunasan biaya program.
                </div>
            </details>
            <details
                class="accordion-item group border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 list-none font-bold text-ultimate-navy dark:text-white"
                >
                    Apakah ada target khusus bagi partner?
                    <span
                        class="material-symbols-outlined text-ultimate-blue transition-transform duration-300 expand-icon"
                        >expand_more</span
                    >
                </summary>
                <div
                    class="p-6 pt-0 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 leading-relaxed"
                >
                    Kami tidak memberikan target minimum pendaftaran. Anda bebas
                    menentukan kapan dan seberapa sering Anda ingin melakukan
                    promosi.
                </div>
            </details>
            <details
                class="accordion-item group border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm"
            >
                <summary
                    class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 list-none font-bold text-ultimate-navy dark:text-white"
                >
                    Metode pembayaran apa yang tersedia?
                    <span
                        class="material-symbols-outlined text-ultimate-blue transition-transform duration-300 expand-icon"
                        >expand_more</span
                    >
                </summary>
                <div
                    class="p-6 pt-0 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 leading-relaxed"
                >
                    Komisi dapat ditarik ke seluruh rekening Bank di Indonesia
                    serta beberapa platform E-Wallet populer.
                </div>
            </details>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
